properties.name: A chart of the sea coasts of New-England, New-Jarsey, Virginia, Maryland and Carolina : from C. Cod to C. Hatteras / by John Seller, hydrogr. to the King ; Iames Clerk sculpsit.
properties.description: from Atlas terrestris, or, A book of mapps of all the empires, monarchies, kingdomes, regions, dominions, principalities, and countreys in the whole world : accomodated with a brief description of the nature and quality of each particular countrey / by Iohn Seller, hydrographer to the Kings most excellent majestie.
